							<h3>Horses are one of the most precious gifts a child can receive. However not everyone can afford to own a horse. So let us give your child a horse experience that everyone can enjoy. Come join the fun at our two-day horse camps. We will start with the basics of grooming, groundwork and safety around horses. Starting a rider in our riding camps allows them to have that one on one time with both a safe horse and a passionate instructor. They will have approximately six hours each day of fun and engaging riding time. In addition our riders will learn proper horse care, exercise, and interaction all while making lifelong friends. So if it's a fun surprise or the perfect gift, we are ready to see everyone have a successful riding career with us at Bay Area Equestrian Center! To hold a spot, call, come on by or book on-line and make your reservations.  Ages 6 and up.</h3>

